                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1414-18450616 t18450616-1414-punishment-144"></join>Transported for Seven Years</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>(There was another indictment against the prisoner.)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Recorder.</hi>
